  "Description": {
    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-commodity\">temporary frigate upgrade</span> that lasts for one expedition.<br><br>The mineral compressor allows fleet mining crews to liquidize the substances they extract, for both faster processing and easier transportation.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "仅限一次远征的<span class=\"name name-commodity\">临时护卫舰升级</span>。<br><br>矿物压缩机能让舰队采矿人员提取的物质液化，以实现更快的处理和更方便的运输。",
    "TencentChinese": "仅限一次远征的<span class=\"name name-commodity\">临时护卫舰升级</span>。<br><br>矿物压缩机能让舰队采矿人员提取的物质液化，以实现更快的处理和更方便的运输。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-commodity\">臨時性巡防艦升級</span>，僅能維持一次的探險。<br><br>礦物壓縮機讓艦隊採礦小組能將萃取的物質轉為液體，不僅能加快處理流程，也更方便運輸。"
  },
